      "text": "Un nu/ muhſu Deewṣ/ klaufi tawa Kalpa Peeluhgſcha- nn un wiṣka Noluḥgfchannu/ un apgaifino tawi Waign pahr tawn fwehtu Weetu/ kas poh- ſtita irr/ ta Kluṅga labbad.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atgreeſ tawn Anſi at Deewṣ! un klaufi/ atwerr ta- was Azzis/ un uſluhko/ ka mehs pohſtiti effam/ un to Bilsfahtu/ kas pehz tawa Wahṛda nofaukts tr. Jo mehs noimettattiees ar muhſu Luḥgfchanahin tawa Preekſchā/ ne muhſas Taitnibas pehz/ bet tawas leelas Schehla- ſibas pehz.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ak Klungs klaufi! ak Klungs peedohd! ak Klungs nemm wehrā! un darri to/ un ne kawejees terwis patcha deht/ mans Deewṣ/ jo taws Bilsfabte in tawi Laudis irr pehz tawa Wahṛda nofaukti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad es wehl runnaju un luḥdsu/ un fatws Grehkus/ un fawu Lauschu Iṣraēta Grehkus iſſuhdfseju/ un ar mannas No- luḥgfchanae preekſch to Klungu mannu Deewu noimettohs/ man- na Deewa fwehta Kalna deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad es ta luḥgdams wehl unnaju/ tad afsrehje tas Wihrs Gabrijels/ fo es Eefahkunā zaur Parahdifchannu bijn redſejs/ un\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un mahẓija manu/ un runnaja ar mannim/ un fazzija: Danijel/ taggad eſmu es iṣgah- jis to Saprafchanutew finnamu darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tu fahzi luḥgt/ tad iṣgahje fchis Wahṛds/ un es ef- tinu nahzis to stahſtiht. Jo tu effi fohti peeneimmigs/ tadeht faproht fcho Wahṛdu/ un nemm wehrā fcho Parahdifchannu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Septindefinits Neddefas irr nosprectas pahr taweem Lau- dim/ un pahr tawu fwehtu Bils- fahtu/ tad tapṣ ta. Pahrkahp- fchana pabeigta/ un tee Grehki aissehgeleti / un ta muhſchiga Taitniba atkat atnefta/ un tahs Parahdifchanas un Pratveefchu Mahzibas aissehgeletas/ un tas Wiſaufwehtajs fwatdihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht finni/ un prohti no ta Wahṛda Iṣeeſchanas/ ka buhs atpakat greestees/ un Je- rusalemi atkat ustaiftht/ lihds Kristu to Leela-Kungu irr fepti- nas Neddefas/ un fechdefinitis un diwi Neddefas/ tad tapṣ tahs Eelas un Muhri atkat ustaiftti/ jepſchu behdigā Laikā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pehz tahm fechdefinitis un diwi Neddefahin taps Kri- ſtus nofauts/ bet ne fewis pehz. Un kadā Leela-Kunga Laudis/ kas atnahks/ famaitahs to Bils- fahtu un to fwehtu Weetu/ ka tam Gats buhs itt ka zaur ne- pluhduſchn Paifumu/ un lihds patc\n"
